  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A two-arm, multicenter, randomized, double-blind, single dose placebo-controlled parallel
      groups study evaluating efficacy and tolerability of 800 mg Acetylsalicylic Acid (Aspirina C)
      in adult patients with a common cold during a two hour in patient phase; and a follow-up
      period of five days of home treatment as required.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
